<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <style>
        body { font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif; }
        .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
        .header { color: #d93025; font-size: 24px; margin-bottom: 20px; }
        .content { line-height: 1.8; color: #333; }
        .btn { display: inline-block; padding: 12px 24px; background-color: #1a73e8; color: #fff; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 4px; margin: 20px 0; }
        .warning { color: #999; font-size: 14px; }
        .footer { margin-top: 30px; padding-top: 20px; border-top: 1px solid #eee; color: #999; font-size: 12px; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">密码重置</div>
        <div class="content">
            <p>{{ username }}，您好！</p>
            <p>请点击下方按钮重置密码（<strong>{{ expire_minutes }}</strong> 分钟内有效）：</p>
            <a class="btn" href="{{ reset_url }}">重置密码</a>
            <p class="warning">如果按钮无法点击，请复制以下链接到浏览器打开：</p>
            <p class="warning"><a href="{{ reset_url }}">{{ reset_url }}</a></p>
            <p class="warning">如果非您本人操作，请忽略此邮件。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>此邮件由系统自动发送，请勿回复。</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
